Package de.hsbremen.tc.tnc.message.m.attribute

Integrity measurement attribute interfaces.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ImAttribute
    Generic integrity measurement attribute base consisting of an attribute header and an attribute value.
    ImAttributeHeader
    Generic integrity measurement attribute header base consisting of a vendor ID and attribute type ID characterizing the attribute.
    ImAttributeHeaderBuilder
    Generic builder base to build an integrity measurement attribute header.
    ImAttributeValue
    Marker to characterize an object as integrity measurement attribute value used by IM(C/V).
    ImAttributeValueBuilder
    Generic builder base to build an integrity measurement attribute value.
